file_contents = 'some test'
bucket = self.test_bucket
key = os.path.join(self.test_folder, 'some-temp-file.txt')
assert self.s3.file_exists(bucket, key) is False
assert self.s3.file_create_from_string(file_contents, bucket, key) is True
assert self.s3.file_exists(bucket, key) is True
assert self.s3.file_contents(bucket, key) == file_contents
assert self.s3.file_delete(bucket, key) is True
